testcase.name: Wallet (e2e) > GET /wallet/credentials > should return a list of credentials
Wallet (e2e) > POST /wallet/credentials > should create a new credential
Wallet (e2e) > POST /wallet/credentials > should return 400 for invalid credential data
Wallet (e2e) > DELETE /wallet/credentials/:id > should delete an existing credential
Wallet (e2e) > DELETE /wallet/credentials/:id > should return 404 for non-existent credential
